We, as researchers, would like to donate $100 to three charities and need your help to distribute them across the following three charities.


Please distribute $100 as you see fit. - <strong>American Society for the Prevention of Cruelty to Animals (ASPCA)</strong>: This organization focuses on animal rescue and protection. They have led the way in fighting cruelty, rescuing and securing adoptions for animals in need, and driving significant legislative change that protects their lives and welfare&mdash;ultimately transforming how Americans value and care for animals.<br />
